and l felt God's breath move through me.

510
00:54:57,092 --> 00:55:01,188
沉入我的胃
And it rolled down into my stomach.

511
00:55:03,166 --> 00:55:05,065
它劈啪作响
lt sloshed around.

512
00:55:06,469 --> 00:55:10,302
我的胃低语着，不是呐喊
And my stomach spoke in a whisper, not a shout,

513
00:55:13,576 --> 00:55:17,773
“用手抚摸这位女士并抚慰她”
''Touch this woman with your hands
and caress her.'' Yes.

514
00:55:22,117 --> 00:55:24,278
亲爱的杭特太太
My dear Mrs. Hunter,

515
00:55:25,454 --> 00:55:27,820
你有关节炎，对吧？
you have arthritis, don't you?

516
00:55:27,956 --> 00:55:29,925
