517
00:55:30,059 --> 00:55:33,653
恶魔在你手上，我会把它拉出来
The devil is in your hands, and l will suck it out.

518
00:55:34,797 --> 00:55:39,166
我不会激动的把这恶魔扔出去
Now, l will not cast this ghost out with a fever

519
00:55:39,302 --> 00:55:44,329
因为在我体内的神灵告诉我，我有新的沟通方法
for the new spirit inside me has shown
me l have a new way to communicate.

520
00:55:46,809 --> 00:55:48,833
就是轻柔的低语
lt is a gentle whisper.

521
00:55:55,217 --> 00:55:57,583
离开吧，恶鬼
Get out of here, ghost.

522
00:56:00,255 --> 00:56:02,588
离开这里，恶鬼
Get out of here, ghost.

523
00:56:04,626 --> 00:56:06,150
离开
Get out.

524
00:56:06,695 --> 00:56:09,563
离开这里，恶鬼
Get out of here, ghost.

525
00:56:11,934 --> 00:56:15,130
离开这里，恶鬼
Get out of here, ghost.

526
00:56:15,237 --> 00:56:19,173
-快进入这位女士的身体 -离开这里，恶鬼
-...and enter this woman's body now.
-Get out of here, ghost.

527
00:56:19,275 --> 00:56:24,110
离开这里，不准你再转身回来
Get out of here. Don't you dare turn
around and come back.

528
00:56:25,313 --> 00:56:26,974
你若胆敢回来
For if you do,

529
00:56:27,083 --> 00:56:32,612
我会用全身神力给你迎头痛击
all the armies of my boot will kick you in the teeth

530
00:56:32,722 --> 00:56:36,213
而你会被扔出去，丢进泥土里
and you will be cast up and thrown in the dirt

531
00:56:36,358 --> 00:56:38,759
一屁股跌回地狱
and thrust back to perdition!

532
00:56:38,860 --> 00:56:42,592
只要我牙齿还在，我要咬穿你
And as long as l have teeth, l will bite you,

533
00:56:42,697 --> 00:56:46,657
就算我没牙齿，也会咬紧双颚
and if l have no teeth, l will gum you!

534
00:56:46,802 --> 00:56:50,500
只要我拳头还在，我会痛揍你
And as long as l have fists, l will bash you!

535
00:56:50,639 --> 00:56:55,338
滚吧，恶鬼!快离开这里!
