-Thank you, Jesus. Thank you, God.

541
00:57:14,864 --> 00:57:17,059
亲爱的杭特太太
My dear Mrs. Hunter.

542
00:57:20,635 --> 00:57:22,570
跟我一起跳舞吧
Dance with me.

543
00:57:29,644 --> 00:57:31,943
-感谢莅临 -真精彩的讲道
-Thanks for coming. -lt was a wonderful sermon.

544
00:57:32,081 --> 00:57:34,447
-明天你会来吗？ -会的
-Will l see you tomorrow? -Yes.

545
00:57:39,454 --> 00:57:40,547
伊莱
Eli.

546
00:57:42,992 --> 00:57:45,789
昨晚井里发生悲剧
Had a tragedy at the well last night.

547
00:57:47,063 --> 00:57:48,724
我听说了
Yes, l heard.

548
00:57:48,831 --> 00:57:51,231
乔根达是虔诚的信徒
Joe Gundha was a man of considerable faith.

549
00:57:51,333 --> 00:57:55,565
如果你想为他祈祷，他的葬礼是明天中午
So if you wish to say a few words,
his burial is at noon tomorrow.

