那有关系吗？
Don't you think that has something to do with this?

557
00:58:08,717 --> 00:58:10,150
这些人需要好好休息
We need these men well-rested to bring in this well.

558
00:58:10,253 --> 00:58:12,447
如果他们听你讲道就不能休息
They can't get that if they're up here
listening to your gospel,

559
00:58:12,554 --> 00:58:14,681
油井就没办法产油...更没办法让大家发财
and then the well can't produce
and blow gold all over the place.

560
00:58:14,789 --> 00:58:16,815
我真希望跟乔多相处些时日
l wish l had more time with Joe Gundha.

561
00:58:16,925 --> 00:58:18,153
该多做些什么的
More could have been done.

562
00:58:18,260 --> 00:58:23,221
那么那口井就不能产油，也不能让大家发财
Then the well can't produce
and blow gold all over the place.

563
