00:58:32,007 --> 00:58:34,135
送还给他的家人，好吗？
find their way back to his family, please?

565
00:58:34,242 --> 00:58:35,766
谢谢
Thank you.

566
00:58:36,244 --> 00:58:39,373
听说你计划改建？
Heard you were planning some renovations.

567
00:58:39,514 --> 00:58:42,483
对，信众数目成长惊人
Yes, our congregation is growing strongly.

568
00:58:43,152 --> 00:58:47,612
-需要更多空间 -刚刚的表演真他妈的精彩
-We need more room.
-That was one goddamn hell of a show.

569
00:58:48,724 --> 00:58:51,284
很高兴有你来访，丹尼尔
We were happy to have you, Daniel.

570
01:00:44,907 --> 01:00:46,771
瓦斯、瓦斯!
Gas, gas, gas!

571
01:00:55,717 --> 01:00:58,811
严禁火花!在这等着!
Lights out! Wait here. Wait here. Lights out!

572
01:01:08,963 --> 01:01:10,760
把火灭了
Put that fire out!

573
01:01:37,626 --> 01:01:41,391
他受伤了吗？H.W.! 把他抱下来给我
ls he hurt? H.W.! Hand him down to me!

574
01:01:45,967 --> 01:01:48,163
-抱下来 -来了
-Hand him down! -Here.

575
01:01:52,340 --> 01:01:54,434
-抱好了？ -我抱好了
-Got him? -l've got him!

576
01:02:01,750 --> 01:02:03,273
天哪
Oh, God.

577
01:02:18,567 --> 01:02:20,090
拜托
Come on.

578
01:02:32,081 --> 01:02:33,775
开门
Open the door.

579
01:02:48,463 --> 01:02:51,228
放手，很好，你很安全
Let go. There you go. You're safe. You're safe.

