587
01:03:14,789 --> 01:03:16,780
我听不见
l can't hear my voice.

588
01:03:25,800 --> 01:03:28,530
我得去解决事情，你在这等我
l have to go and deal with this now.
You wait here for me.

589
01:03:28,637 --> 01:03:32,436
你明白吗？在这等我，我马上回来，就一下子
You understand? You wait here for me.
l'll be back. l'll be back in a minute.

590
01:03:32,574 --> 01:03:33,735
-在这等着 -不要走
-Wait here. -Don't leave!

591
01:03:33,842 --> 01:03:37,902
我会照顾你的，在这等着，儿子，我要去灭火
l'm going to take care of you. Wait.
Stay here, son. l'm going to fix this.

592
01:03:38,012 --> 01:03:39,275
-不要走 -你不会有事的
-Don't leave! -You're going to be fine!

593
01:03:39,414 --> 01:03:40,438
在这等着
Wait for me here!

594
01:03:40,548 --> 01:03:43,518
-抱住他、抱住他 -不要走
-Hold him down. Hold him down. -Don't leave!

595
01:03:45,753 --> 01:03:48,382
切断绳索，丹尼尔
Got to break the cables, Daniel!

596
01:03:48,556 --> 01:03:50,387
给我锤子
Get me a hammer!

597
01:03:56,731 --> 01:03:58,597
给我一把锤子
Get me a hammer!

598
01:04:01,103 --> 01:04:02,831
在这里
Here you go.

599
01:04:28,130 --> 01:04:29,653
退后
Get back!

600
01:05:07,101 --> 01:05:08,432
-麦可 -老板
-Michael! -Sir!

601
01:05:08,536 --> 01:05:10,971
带戴维和两个人
Take Dave and two of the fellas,
pick up some hoses...

602
01:05:11,072 --> 01:05:15,009
比利，保护屋顶，太烫就离开
Billy, protect the roof.
Don't wait before it gets too hot.

603
01:05:37,365 --> 01:05:39,994
你干嘛满脸愁容？
What are you looking so miserable about?

604
01:05:40,101 --> 01:05:42,969
我们脚下有无尽的藏油
There's a whole ocean of oil under our feet!

605
01:05:43,072 --> 01:05:45,733
除了你，没人能帮我挖出来
No one can get at it except for me.

606
01:06:32,521 --> 01:06:34,454
H.W.还好吧？
H.W. okay?

607
01:06:35,123 --> 01:06:36,681
他不好
No, he isn't.

608
01:06:38,960 --> 01:06:41,293
-他在哪里？ -餐厅
-Where is he? -Mess room.

609
