我们什么时候可以拿到钱？
When do we get our money, Daniel?

630
01:13:29,238 --> 01:13:32,765
你不是治疗者吗？你不是神灵选中的人？
Aren't you a healer? And a vessel for the Holy Spirit?

631
01:13:32,942 --> 01:13:35,911
你何时要来让我儿子恢复听力？
When are you coming over and make my son hear again?

632
01:13:36,045 --> 01:13:37,204
你做不到？
Can't you do that?

633
01:13:37,313 --> 01:13:39,280
若让我为井祈福，这就不会发生
lf you had let me bless the well,
this wouldn't have happened.

634
01:13:39,381 --> 01:13:42,180
-丹尼尔 -你不该这么做的
-Daniel. -You shouldn't have done that.

635
