You've let someone come in here
and walk all over us.

643
01:15:18,581 --> 01:15:23,041
你让他来，在这里开挖石油
You let him in and do his work here,

644
01:15:23,152 --> 01:15:27,118
你这个笨蛋却廉价贱卖土地
and you are a stupid man for what we could have had.

645
01:15:27,289 --> 01:15:31,225
我遵照上帝旨意，我试过
l followed His word, Eli. l tried.

646
01:15:31,327 --> 01:15:34,056
你啥都没做，只是呆坐家中
You didn't do anything but sit down.

647
01:15:35,430 --> 01:15:37,899
你既懒又蠢
You're lazy, and you're stupid.

648
01:15:41,604 --> 01:15:45,734
