653
01:16:04,092 --> 01:16:09,087
闭上你的嘴，亚伯! 都怪你那个笨儿子
Shut your mouth, Abel! lt was your stupid son!

654
01:16:09,265 --> 01:16:13,201
是保罗叫他来的，我知道
lt was Paul who told him to come here. l know it.

655
01:16:13,301 --> 01:16:15,030
他跑去找他，还说...
He went to him and he said,

656
01:16:15,136 --> 01:16:19,869
“我愚蠢的父亲会卖出他的地”
''My stupid, weak father will give away his lots.

657
01:16:19,975 --> 01:16:23,434
