''Go and take him.'' And you let it happen.

658
01:16:27,984 --> 01:16:31,078
真是一对呆瓜父子
A stupid father to a stupid son.

659
01:16:36,759 --> 01:16:38,420
滚出去
Get out of there!

660
01:17:09,125 --> 01:17:11,059
需要我效劳吗？
Can l help you?

661
01:17:12,293 --> 01:17:13,851
丹尼尔？
Daniel?

662
01:17:13,962 --> 01:17:17,659
-你是谁？ -我叫亨利
-Who's that? -My name is Henry.

663
01:17:18,634 --> 01:17:20,295
什么事？
Yeah?

664
01:17:21,203 --> 01:17:22,863
我是亨利
l'm Henry.

665
01:17:24,140 --> 01:17:26,266
