-Yes, sir, that's right.

672
01:18:25,634 --> 01:18:30,765
我在报上看过你油井的报导，关于你的成功
l read about your gusher in the paper, about your success.

673
01:18:30,939 --> 01:18:33,931
你听说我成功？就跑来要钱？
You heard about my strike? You just show up?

674
01:18:34,976 --> 01:18:36,911
我们的父亲死了
Our father's dead.

675
01:18:38,380 --> 01:18:41,577
我听说恩尼斯死了，我想找你
Ernest died, l heard. l wanted to find you.

676
01:18:41,716 --> 01:18:43,377
什么时候？
When?

677
01:18:43,485 --> 01:18:47,081
三个月前，我收到安娜贝的信
Three months ago. l got a letter from Annabelle.

678
01:18:48,056 --> 01:18:49,990
我妹妹安娜贝？
My sister, Annabelle?

679
01:18:51,961 --> 01:18:55,590
-她在哪里？ -还在家乡，方达勒克
-Where is she? -Still at home. Fond du Lac.

680
01:18:57,332 --> 01:19:00,791
你大老远跑来跟我说这个？
You came all the way from Wisconsin to tell me this?

681
01:19:00,970 --> 01:19:03,962
我从新墨西哥来的，我住过那里
l'm coming from New Mexico. l've been there.

682
01:19:05,173 --> 01:19:07,073
我是来找你的
l came to find you.

683
01:19:08,176 --> 01:19:10,235
你知道我的事吗？
Did you know about me?

684
01:19:18,453 --> 01:19:20,649
你有身份证明吗？
Do you have identification?

685
01:19:21,323 --> 01:19:23,416
你有这封信吗？
Do you have this letter?

686
01:19:46,481 --> 01:19:48,574
-你是从哪里来的？ -新墨西哥州
-Where are you coming from? -From New Mexico.

687
01:19:48,684 --> 01:19:51,118
我知道，那里的哪里？
Yes, l know, but from where?

688
01:19:51,252 --> 01:19:54,279
银矿市，我在那里待过两年
Silver City. l've been there for two years.

689
01:19:55,356 --> 01:20:00,158
我尝试过自己钻油好几年
l was trying drilling of my own for years.

690
01:20:00,261 --> 01:20:06,689
-在德州、路易斯安那都租过地 -有什么成果吗？
-Getting leases in Texas. Louisiana.
-Anything that produced?

691
01:20:06,835 --> 01:20:09,804
没有，不像你那么成功
No. Not like your success, no.

692
01:20:16,311 --> 01:20:18,712
-你结婚没？ -没有
-Are you married? -No.

693
01:20:19,247 --> 01:20:23,207
我坐过牢，我有过一段悲惨的日子
l spent time in jail. l had a stretch of very bad time.

694
01:20:23,918 --> 01:20:27,115
身无分文，在路易斯安那被捕
l had nothing. l was picked up in Louisiana.

695
01:20:28,591 --> 01:20:32,220
我在外役监服役半年修筑马路
l worked on a chain gang for six months building roads.

696
01:20:32,761 --> 01:20:35,957
那一段日子...很辛苦
That was a very hard time.

697
01:20:39,734 --> 01:20:41,532
你结婚没？
Are you married?

698
01:20:42,805 --> 01:20:45,204
你为什么会坐牢？
What were you in jail for?

699
01:20:45,341 --> 01:20:49,868
信不信由你，我做了那么多糟糕的事
Believe it or not, for all the
terrible things l've gotten myself into,

700
01:20:50,011 --> 01:20:53,503
但我被逮捕时，却啥都没做
when they picked me up, l hadn't done anything.

701
01:20:53,649 --> 01:20:57,380
不过我做过许多事
But l've done my share of things

702
01:20:59,721 --> 01:21:02,122
不该公开谈论
that shouldn't be talked about.

703
01:21:24,579 --> 01:21:27,673
喝吧，喝掉
Drink it. Drink it!

704
01:22:10,259 --> 01:22:11,783
睡吧
Come on.

705
01:22:43,225 --> 01:22:44,817
所以...
So...

706
01:22:49,331 --> 01:22:51,127
你要什么？
What do you want, Henry?

707
01:22:53,534 --> 01:22:55,127
没什么
Nothing.

708
01:22:58,073 --> 01:23:02,270
如果你能付我钱，我可以为你效劳
lf you can spare something, l can work for you in any way.

709
01:23:02,377 --> 01:23:06,677
我知道我会继续前进，没多久就会回故乡去
l know l'll keep moving, before long,
to get back to Fond du Lac.

710
01:23:07,716 --> 01:23:10,082
-你有钱吗？ -有一些
-Do you have any money? -Some.

711
01:23:11,153 --> 01:23:13,314
-不多 -直接回答我
-Not much. -Just answer me directly.

712
01:23:13,454 --> 01:23:17,015
没有，就说你想留下来工作
You say ''nothing,'' then you say
you'd like to stay and work.

713
01:23:17,158 --> 01:23:22,095
更好的是，我希望听到你说你想留下来
And it's better, l'd just like to hear
you say you'd like to be here.

714
01:23:23,198 --> 01:23:25,097
我想留下来
l'd like to be here.

715
01:23:30,471 --> 01:23:36,069
我是个好工人。我做过钻油架、建过铁路
l'm a good worker. l worked cable tool rigs, built railroads.

716
01:23:38,212 --> 01:23:40,238
我不需要帮忙
l won't need any favors.

717
01:23:45,287 --> 01:23:46,810
很好
Good.

718
01:24:12,280 --> 01:24:14,408
我母亲知道些什么？
What did my mother know?

719
01:24:17,019 --> 01:24:18,680
我不知道
I don't know.

720
01:24:19,220 --> 01:24:23,783
我不知她知不知道，换个角度想，也许她根本不知道
I don't know if she knew and looked
the other way, if she never knew.

721
01:24:26,528 --> 01:24:28,393
你为何离开？
Why did you leave?

722
01:24:30,265 --> 01:24:33,234
我知道你跟我们的爸爸处不好
I know you didn't get on with our father.

723
01:24:38,372 --> 01:24:42,139
我为地理调查组织工作去了堪萨斯
l worked for Geological Survey and went to Kansas.

724
01:24:44,546 --> 01:24:47,605
我在那待不下去，我就是没办法
l couldn't stay there. l just couldn't.

725
01:24:49,350 --> 01:24:51,876
我不喜欢自我辩解
l don't like to explain myself.

726
01:24:57,926 --> 01:25:02,158
-亨利，你很容易生气吗？ -气什么？
-Are you an angry man, Henry? -About what?

727
01:25:02,997 --> 01:25:06,764
你嫉妒心重吗？你会嫉妒吗？
Are you envious? Do you get envious?

728
01:25:08,036 --> 01:25:10,003
我不这么想，不会
l don't think so, no.

729
01:25:14,475 --> 01:25:16,807
我天生爱出头
l have a competition in me.

730
01:25:18,012 --> 01:25:20,447
我不要别人成功
l want no one else to succeed.

731
01:25:25,487 --> 01:25:29,980
-我痛恨大部分的人 -那部份的我已经死了
-l hate most people. -That part of me is gone.

732
01:25:31,193 --> 01:25:34,094
工作和不成功
Working and not succeeding,

733
01:25:34,195 --> 01:25:38,189
所有的...失败都让我...
all my failures have left me...

734
01:25:41,235 --> 01:25:43,100
我不在乎了
l just don't care.

735
01:25:44,805 --> 01:25:47,399
如果我有，你就有
Well, if it's in me, it's in you.

736
01:25:48,944 --> 01:25:54,314
我有时候看着人们，却看不到值得喜欢的特点
There are times when l look at people
and l see nothing worth liking.

737
01:26:00,322 --> 01:26:04,382
我想赚到足够的钱，远离所有人
l want to earn enough money l can get away from everyone.

738
01:26:09,430 --> 01:26:11,899
你要拿你的孩子怎么办？
What will you do about your boy?

739
01:26:19,640 --> 01:26:21,268
我不知道
l don't know.

740
01:26:22,810 --> 01:26:25,244
也许情况会改变
Maybe it'll change.

741
01:26:25,413 --> 01:26:29,783
人的听力会恢复吗？我不知道，也许也没人知道
Does your sound come back to you?
l don't know. Maybe no one knows that.

742
01:26:29,952 --> 01:26:34,115
-医生也许也不知道 -他母亲呢？
-Doctor might not know that. -Where's his mother?

743
01:26:40,095 --> 01:26:43,087
我不想谈我的私事
l don't want to talk about those things.

744
01:26:46,467 --> 01:26:48,698
我很清楚人性的黑暗面
l see the worst in people, Henry.

745
01:26:50,738 --> 01:26:54,573
我不需要认识他们就能知道
l don't need to look past seeing them to get all l need.

746
01:26:56,744 --> 01:27:00,703
多年来我逐渐的建立了我的仇恨感
l've built up my hatreds over the years, little by little.

747
01:27:04,418 --> 01:27:07,752
你的到来给了我第二股能量
Having you here gives me a second breath of life.

748
01:27:08,957 --> 01:27:11,585
我不能继续靠自己打拼
l can't keep doing this on my own

749
01:27:14,895 --> 01:27:19,923
跟这些烂人
with these people.

750
01:27:59,740 --> 01:28:02,265
丹尼尔!丹尼尔，醒醒!丹尼尔!
Daniel! Daniel, wake up! Daniel!

751
01:29:44,613 --> 01:29:48,104
我要去跟车掌说句话
Just have to go and have a word with the conductor.

752
01:29:48,850 --> 01:29:50,976
我马上回来
l'll be right back.

753
01:29:51,086 --> 01:29:55,819
你待在这里，明白吗？待在这里
You stay here. You understand? You stay here.

754
01:29:56,858 --> 01:29:58,689
我马上回来
l'll be right back.

755
01:30:51,412 --> 01:30:53,278
不!不!
No! No!

756
01:30:54,983 --> 01:30:56,506
不!
No!

757
01:31:06,027 --> 01:31:07,585
-提佛 -普兰优
-Tilford! -Plainview.

758
01:31:07,695 --> 01:31:09,993
这是我弟弟，亨利普兰优
This is my brother, Henry Plainview from Fond du Lac.

759
01:31:10,131 --> 01:31:11,757
我是提佛，幸会
H.M. Tilford. Pleasure.

760
01:31:11,867 --> 01:31:14,335
亨利普兰优...卡特
Henry Plainview. J.J. Carter.

761
01:31:16,371 --> 01:31:17,770
那么...
So...

762
01:31:17,872 --> 01:31:19,806
-开始吧？ -好的
-Shall we? -Yes.

763
01:31:27,681 --> 01:31:29,912
你儿子好吗？
How's your boy?

764
01:31:30,018 --> 01:31:33,418
-多谢你关心 -我们帮得上什么忙吗？
-Thank you for asking. -ls there anything we can do?

765
01:31:33,520 --> 01:31:35,921
关心就够了
Thanks for asking is enough.

766
01:31:37,626 --> 01:31:39,594
你有什么计划？
So what are your plans?

767
01:31:41,363 --> 01:31:44,594
你们是想买我这里的土地？
ls this about buying up my tracts here?

768
01:31:44,733 --> 01:31:45,791
对
Yes.

769
01:31:45,900 --> 01:31:48,698
电报提的是我在灰狼坡的地
The cable was about my Coyote Hills lease.

770
01:31:48,869 --> 01:31:53,068
-我们也想买那里 -灰狼坡的地你出价多少？
-We'd like that, too.
-What's your offer on Coyote Hills?

771
01:31:53,173 --> 01:31:57,735
-我们出15万买所有的权利 -我接受，接下来呢？
-We'll offer 1 50,000 for full title.
-That's a deal. What's next?

772
01:31:58,613 --> 01:32:02,981
你在小波士顿有一万一千备地。你有一口能产油的井
You have 11 ,000 acres in Little Boston.
You have one proven well

773
01:32:03,083 --> 01:32:04,948
-先前出了事 -我有三口能产油的井
-that was damaged... -l have three wells proven.

774
01:32:05,052 --> 01:32:08,954
你根本没查清楚，是三口井
You haven't been paying attention. That's three proven wells.

775
01:32:13,228 --> 01:32:17,561
我们一分钟内就能让你成为富翁
We'll make you a millionaire while you're sitting here
from one minute to the next.

776
01:32:19,434 --> 01:32:22,163
那我接下来要做什么？
And what else would l do with myself?

777
01:32:23,939 --> 01:32:28,273
-你问我？ -我还能做什么？
-Are you asking me? -What else would l do with myself?

778
01:32:28,877 --> 01:32:31,003
照顾你儿子
Take care of your son.

779
01:32:32,680 --> 01:32:35,149
我不知道你要做什么
l don't know what you would do.

780
01:32:37,719 --> 01:32:40,186
若你是我，标准石油花一百万
lf you were me and Standard
offered to buy what you had

781
01:32:40,354 --> 01:32:43,051
买你所拥有的一切，为什么？
for a million dollars, why? So, why?

782
01:32:44,259 --> 01:32:45,385
你知道原因
You know why.

783
01:32:45,493 --> 01:32:47,358
你该自己去挖掘
Yeah, you fellas should just scratch around in the dirt

784
01:32:47,462 --> 01:32:50,828
像我们一样找油，而不是买下别人的心血
and find it like the rest of us, instead of
buying up someone else's hard work.

785
01:32:50,998 --> 01:32:52,932
我挖过，孩子
l've scratched around the dirt, son.

786
01:32:53,033 --> 01:32:55,059
你要改变你的运输成本？
You going to change your shipping costs?

787
01:32:55,170 --> 01:32:58,139
运送成本不由我们决定，是铁路
We don't dictate shipping costs. That's railroad business.

788
01:32:59,173 --> 01:33:01,801
你们没买下铁路啊？
You don't own the railroads?

789
01:33:05,814 --> 01:33:08,373
你们当然买下了
'Course you do. Of course you do.

790
01:33:10,085 --> 01:33:12,484
你要把油运到哪里？
Where you going to put it all?

791
01:33:13,587 --> 01:33:15,180
哪里？
Where?

792
01:33:16,858 --> 01:33:20,885
建输油管？找联合石油？随便你
Build a pipeline? Make a deal
with Union Oil? Be my guest.

793
01:33:20,996 --> 01:33:22,690
不过你若无法成功
But if you can't pull it off,

794
01:33:22,796 --> 01:33:26,823
你脚下有再多油也卖不出去
you've got an ocean of oil
under your feet with nowhere to go.

795
01:33:27,868 --> 01:33:32,533
何不卖给我们？我们能让你发财
Why not turn it over to us? We'll make you rich.

796
01:33:32,640 --> 01:33:34,938
你就好好陪你儿子吧
You spend time with your boy.

797
01:33:36,011 --> 01:33:38,137
这是个伟大的发现
lt's a great discovery.

798
01:33:39,079 --> 01:33:41,207
让我们帮你吧
Now, let us help you.

799
01:33:50,358 --> 01:33:53,485
你这是教我怎么经营我的家庭？
Did you just tell me how to run my family?

800
01:33:53,595 --> 01:33:55,789
这可能比找到石油还重要
lt might be more important now
that you've proven the field

801
01:33:55,930 --> 01:33:57,795
而我们想帮你
and we're offering to buy you out.

802
01:33:57,931 --> 01:34:00,162
有一天我会去找你，摸进你家
One night l'm going to come to you,
inside of your house,

803
01:34:00,268 --> 01:34:03,237
或你睡觉的地方，割了你的喉咙
or wherever you're sleeping,
and l'm going to cut your throat.

804
01:34:03,337 --> 01:34:04,930
什么？
What?

805
01:34:05,273 --> 01:34:06,364
你说什么？你疯了吗？
What are you talking about? Have you gone crazy?

806
01:34:06,474 --> 01:34:08,135
-你听见我说的话了？ -我听见了
-Did you hear what l said? -l heard what you said,

807
01:34:08,243 --> 01:34:10,541
- 你干嘛这么说？-不准你教我怎么养儿子
-why did you say it?
-You don't tell me about my son.

808
01:34:10,645 --> 01:34:12,840
你干嘛抓狂又威胁要杀我？
Why are you acting insane
and threatening to cut my throat?

809
01:34:12,947 --> 01:34:16,006
-不准你教我怎么养儿子 -我没教你任何事
-You don't tell me about my son.
-l'm not telling you anything!

810
01:34:16,117 --> 01:34:19,917
我要你讲理，若有冒犯，我道歉
l'm asking you to be reasonable.
lf l've offended you, l apologize.

811
01:34:20,055 --> 01:34:22,216
等着看我有何能耐吧
You'll see what l can do.

812
01:34:29,997 --> 01:34:34,195
这一小块地是哈普拥有的三千备牧场
This parcel here is the 3,000-acre
ranch owned by B.L. Harper.

813
01:34:34,335 --> 01:34:36,826
这是圣路易斯郡的土地
This is San Luis Obispo County land.

814
01:34:37,005 --> 01:34:38,801
从这里到海边，都是联合石油的
And from here to the coast, it's all Union Oil.

815
01:34:38,907 --> 01:34:42,034
这是什么？这怎么不是我的？
What's this? Why don't l own this?

816
01:34:45,012 --> 01:34:49,574
-这怎么不是我的？ -那是班迪的地
-Why don't l own this?
-That's the Bandy tract.

817
01:34:50,385 --> 01:34:53,547
我们在买地时，他拒绝出售
He was the holdout, when we were doing the buying.

818
01:34:53,688 --> 01:34:56,087
他原本想跟你谈
He had hoped to speak with you.

819
01:35:00,295 --> 01:35:03,752
不能在这块地附近建输油管吗？
Can't you just build the pipeline around this tract?

820
01:35:06,768 --> 01:35:10,795
我能在第赫求庇山脉周围建五十哩的输油管吗？
Can l build around 50 miles of Tehachapi mountains?

821
01:35:10,939 --> 01:35:13,463
别在我面前耍白痴
Don't be thick in front of me, Al.

822
01:35:14,109 --> 01:35:17,805
-我可以再去找他 -不，我去跟那个人谈
-l can go to him again. -No, l'll go and talk to the man.

823
01:35:17,945 --> 01:35:20,846
我去谈，让你看看怎么做才对
l'll talk to him. Show you how it's done.

824
01:35:24,685 --> 01:35:27,086
好，打包行李吧，亨利
All right. Pack it up, Henry.

825
01:35:37,431 --> 01:35:41,368
-他房间有多大？ -他跟另一个孩子住一间
-How big is his room?
-He's sharing with another boy.

826
01:35:41,469 --> 01:35:44,336
-谁？ -比他大的孩子，大约12岁
-Who? -An older boy. About 1 2.

827
01:35:44,439 --> 01:35:47,430
他已经待一年了，叫巴朗
He's been there for a year. Named Ballard.

828
01:35:52,680 --> 01:35:57,048
-房间有多大？ -够大了，有足够的空间
-How big is the room?
-lt's a fair size. Got enough space.

829
01:35:59,386 --> 01:36:02,652
你要带亨利去见联合石油的人？
Are you taking Henry with you to meet Union Oil?

830
01:36:15,869 --> 01:36:19,498
-你是威廉班迪的儿子？ -孙子
-Are you the son of William Bandy? -Grandson.

831
01:36:19,606 --> 01:36:21,404
-他在吗？ -他出去了
-ls he here? -No, he's out.

832
01:36:21,509 --> 01:36:22,600
他人在哪里？
Where is he?

833
01:36:22,710 --> 01:36:25,542
我说他出去了，你要干嘛？
Told you, he's out. Now, what do you want?

834
01:36:29,050 --> 01:36:32,985
我叫丹尼尔普兰优，我想跟他谈谈他的地
l'm Daniel Plainview. l want to talk
with him about his property.

835
01:36:33,087 --> 01:36:37,989
-谈什么？ -我想我会跟他当面谈
-About what? -l believe l'll talk with him about that.

836
01:36:38,426 --> 01:36:40,859
-你就是那个石油商人？ -是的
-You're that oilman, aren't you? -That's right.

837
01:36:41,029 --> 01:36:42,997
我们不要你来这里乱挖
We don't want you drilling out here.

838
01:36:43,096 --> 01:36:46,497
我也不要，他什么时候回来？
l don't want it either. Now, when will he be back?

839
01:36:46,600 --> 01:36:47,658
过几天
Few days.

840
01:36:47,769 --> 01:36:50,328
告诉他我想跟他谈，不谈挖地
Tell him l'd like to speak with him. Not about drilling.

841
01:36:50,438 --> 01:36:52,667
我一个礼拜后再来
And l'll be back in a week.

842
01:39:11,779 --> 01:39:13,905
把那放进玻璃框里
Put that in a glass case.

843
01:39:14,782 --> 01:39:16,681
敬联合石油
Here's to Union Oil.

844
01:39:17,385 --> 01:39:18,476
数百哩的输油管
Hundred miles of pipeline,

845
01:39:18,586 --> 01:39:20,917
和本国所有的个人油商
and all the independent producers of this great state.

846
01:39:21,055 --> 01:39:22,180
干杯
Cheers.

847
01:39:47,247 --> 01:39:49,944
方达勒克有间房子
There's that house in Fond du Lac

848
01:39:51,886 --> 01:39:55,117
约翰霍利建的，你记得吗？
that John Hollister built. Do you remember it?

849
01:39:57,992 --> 01:40:01,427
我小时候认为那是我看过的最美的房子
l thought as a boy that was
the most beautiful house l'd ever seen,

850
01:40:01,529 --> 01:40:03,155
我想要它
and l wanted it.

851
01:40:03,930 --> 01:40:06,399
我想住在里面
l wanted to live in it.

852
01:40:06,501 --> 01:40:08,229
在里面吃饭
And eat in it.

853
01:40:08,869 --> 01:40:10,462
清扫它
And clean it.

854
01:40:13,474 --> 01:40:17,774
就算还只是个孩子，我也想让自己的孩子在附近奔跑
And even as a boy, l wanted
to have children to run around in it.

855
01:40:19,479 --> 01:40:22,210
你现在想要什么都能拥有了
You can have anything you'd like now, Daniel.

856
01:40:22,917 --> 01:40:24,645
你也该拥有
And you should.

857
01:40:25,319 --> 01:40:29,983
-你想在哪里建房子？ -这里，也许吧，靠近海边
-Where are you going to build it?
-Here, maybe. Near the ocean.

858
01:40:32,926 --> 01:40:35,690
你想建一栋一模一样的房子？
Would you make it look like that house?

859
01:40:40,435 --> 01:40:43,893
我现在要是看到那栋房子会吐
l think if l saw that house now, it'd make me sick.

860
01:40:50,344 --> 01:40:52,811
我们可以用餐，再找几个女人
We can eat and get some women.

861
01:40:55,750 --> 01:40:57,877
带她们去桃树舞厅跳舞
Take them to the Peachtree dance.

862
01:41:01,689 --> 01:41:05,625
我说灌醉她们再带她们去跳舞
l say get liquored up and take them
to the Peachtree dance.

863
01:41:08,496 --> 01:41:09,962
好
Yeah.

864
01:42:28,676 --> 01:42:31,076
你能给我一点钱吗？
Can l have some money, please?

865
01:42:38,485 --> 01:42:40,920
你能给我一点钱吗？
Can l have some money, please?

866
01:43:29,970 --> 01:43:32,462
我要你告诉我一件事
l want you to tell me something.

867
01:43:36,143 --> 01:43:37,804
什么事？
What?

868
01:43:38,345 --> 01:43:41,804
那房子旁边的牧场叫什么名字？
What's the name of the farm next to the Hill House?

869
01:43:53,027 --> 01:43:57,657
那房子旁边的牧场叫什么名字？
What was the name of the farm next to the Hill House?

870
01:44:01,202 --> 01:44:04,194
-我不记得了 -你是谁？
-l can't remember... -Who are you?

871
01:44:07,173 --> 01:44:09,108
我会走的，丹尼尔
l'll leave, Daniel.

872
01:44:10,810 --> 01:44:12,471
你是谁？
Who are you?

873
01:44:15,750 --> 01:44:17,479
我谁都不是
l'm no one.

874
01:44:18,319 --> 01:44:20,582
让我起来离开吧
Just let me get up and go.

875
01:44:22,890 --> 01:44:24,755
我有弟弟吗？
Do l have a brother?

876
01:44:28,729 --> 01:44:33,927
我在国王城认识一个人，他说他是你弟弟
l met a man in King City who said he was your brother.

877
01:44:36,470 --> 01:44:39,564
我们当了几个月的朋友
We were friends for months.

878
01:44:41,074 --> 01:44:42,975
在国王城工作
Working in King City.

879
01:44:45,179 --> 01:44:48,113
他想设法来找你
And he wanted to make his way to you, Daniel.

880
01:44:49,350 --> 01:44:51,476
我们身无分文
We didn't have any money.

881
