我之前有请你来找我谈
l had asked for you to come and talk to me before.

900
01:49:24,958 --> 01:49:27,189
当时你正在租地
When you were leasing land.

901
01:49:28,462 --> 01:49:30,259
没错，是的
That's right, yes.

902
01:49:31,966 --> 01:49:34,457
我儿子生了重病
My boy's been very sick, you know.

903
01:49:35,636 --> 01:49:38,127
这是在你儿子生病之前
This was before your boy got sick.

904
01:49:41,274 --> 01:49:48,646
我知道
你想在我的土地上建输油管
Now, l know that you would like to build a pipeline
through my property.

905
01:49:48,748 --> 01:49:52,845
-我听说的没错吧？ -完全正确
-ls that right, what l've heard?
-lt's absolutely right. And,

906
01:49:53,554 --> 01:49:54,645
这个
well...

907
01:49:55,756 --> 01:49:59,020
八寸的油管，有你同意就可以埋设
Eight inch pipe. lt could be buried with your consent.

908
01:49:59,126 --> 01:50:01,685
我向你保证绝对不会破裂
l guarantee you absolutely no disruption...

909
01:50:01,795 --> 01:50:03,319
上帝
God.

910
01:50:04,864 --> 01:50:07,425
上帝跟我说过你该怎么做
God has told me what you must do.

911
01:50:11,805 --> 01:50:13,670
该怎么做呢？
And what is that?

912
01:50:14,507 --> 01:50:18,409
你该接受耶稣基督的洗礼
You should be washed in the blood of Jesus Christ.

913
01:50:20,247 --> 01:50:22,146
但我受洗过了
But l am.

914
01:50:23,684 --> 01:50:26,345
我受洗过了，班迪先生
l have been washed, Mr. Bandy. l have been.

915
01:50:26,520 --> 01:50:32,185
那是你救赎的唯一方法,也是你达成目标的唯一方法
lt's your only way to salvation.
And your only way for what you want.

916
