你可以在第三启示教堂受洗
You can take it at the Church of the Third Revelation.

917
01:50:40,067 --> 01:50:42,034
我付你三千元
l'll pay you $3,000.

918
01:50:44,704 --> 01:50:47,469
我希望你成为我们教堂的一员
l'd like you to be part of our church.

919
01:50:49,376 --> 01:50:51,240
我付你五千元
l'll pay you $5,000.

920
01:50:52,378 --> 01:50:53,970
受洗吧
Be baptized.

921
