l wish everyone could be saved, but they won't. No, they won't.

930
01:52:23,970 --> 01:52:27,429
你永远不会获得救赎，如果你...
You will never be saved if you...

931
01:52:27,541 --> 01:52:29,509
拒绝接受主
Reject the blood.

932
01:52:30,344 --> 01:52:31,868
很好
Good.

933
01:52:32,546 --> 01:52:37,006
现在，有罪人想获得救赎吗？
Now, is there a sinner here looking for salvation?

934
01:52:39,720 --> 01:52:41,448
新的成员？
A new member?

935
01:52:45,792 --> 01:52:47,520
我再问一次
l'll ask it again.

936
01:52:49,563 --> 01:52:52,225
有罪人来此寻求上帝吗？
ls there a sinner here looking for God?

937
01:52:52,365 --> 01:52:53,890
是的
Yes.

938
01:52:57,671 --> 01:52:59,262
让我来
Allow me.

939
01:53:01,341 --> 01:53:04,070
谢谢你的光临，丹尼尔兄弟
Thank you for coming, brother Daniel.

940
01:53:06,246 --> 01:53:07,975
谢谢，伊莱
Thank you, Eli.

941
01:53:09,015 --> 01:53:14,113
我们这里有个罪人，他希望获得救赎
We have a sinner with us here who wishes for salvation!

942
01:53:14,253 --> 01:53:17,814
-丹尼尔，你是罪人吗？ -是的
-Daniel, are you a sinner? -Yes.

943
01:53:17,957 --> 01:53:20,619
主上听不见你，丹尼尔
The Lord can't hear you, Daniel.

944
01:53:20,761 --> 01:53:24,560
告诉他，去跟他说，没关系的
Say it to Him. Go ahead and speak to him. lt's all right.

945
01:53:25,364 --> 01:53:27,662
-是的 -双膝跪地
-Yes. -Down on your knees.

946
01:53:27,801 --> 01:53:29,462
向他祷告
Pray to Him.

947
01:53:30,703 --> 01:53:35,106
仰望天空说出来
Look up to the sky and say it.

948
01:53:37,711 --> 01:53:39,837
