可是也带来你的坏习惯
but you have also brought your bad habits as a backslider.

951
01:53:49,823 --> 01:53:54,088
你勾引女性又遗弃孩子
You've lusted after women,
and you have abandoned your child.

952
01:53:54,194 --> 01:53:57,253
你的孩子，你抚养又遗弃
Your child, that you raised, you have abandoned

953
01:53:57,363 --> 01:53:59,797
只因他病了，因此你有罪
all because he was sick and you have sinned.

954
01:53:59,932 --> 01:54:02,094
大声说吧，我是罪人
So say it now. l am a sinner.

955
01:54:02,202 --> 01:54:04,101
-我是罪人 -大声一点
-l am a sinner. -Say it louder.

956
01:54:04,203 --> 01:54:06,934
-我是罪人 -我是罪人
-l am a sinner. -l am a sinner.

957
01:54:07,073 --> 01:54:09,007
