Out, devil! Out, sin!

976
01:55:03,663 --> 01:55:06,224
-让我感受主的力量 -你接受
-Let me feel the power of the Lord, Eli.
-Do you accept

977
01:55:06,332 --> 01:55:10,234
第三启示教堂导引你吗？
the Church of the Third Revelation as your spiritual guide?

978
01:55:11,771 --> 01:55:15,935
