01:58:32,639 --> 01:58:34,731
我抱不动你了
You're too heavy for me.

1011
01:58:37,810 --> 01:58:40,506
你想吃点什么吗？
Do you want to get something to eat?

1012
01:58:41,715 --> 01:58:46,015
那是输油管，看到没？一路直达大海
That's the pipeline, see? All the way to the sea.

1013
01:59:07,106 --> 01:59:08,664
过来
Come here.

1014
01:59:15,548 --> 01:59:17,413
我爱你，儿子
l love you, son.

1015
01:59:19,219 --> 01:59:21,345
让我好好看看你
Let's take a look at you.

1016
01:59:23,657 --> 01:59:26,489
好了，够了、够了
All right. That's it, that's it. That's it.

1017
01:59:50,583 --> 01:59:53,882
我们帮你弄点好吃的吧
Let's get some decent food inside of you.

1018
01:59:54,020 --> 01:59:57,819
我们就需要这个, 好吃营养又昂贵的餐点
That's all we need here is a good, strong, expensive meal.

1019
01:59:58,425 --> 02:00:00,154
你饿了吗？
You hungry?

1020
02:00:01,027 --> 02:00:02,288
-服务生？ -是，先生
-Waiter? -Yes, sir.

1021
02:00:02,395 --> 02:00:05,228
两份牛排，一杯威士忌，给他水
Two steaks, a whiskey, and water for him.

1022
02:00:06,865 --> 02:00:09,356
-还有羊奶 -好的，先生
-And goat's milk. -Very good, sir.

1023
02:00:16,208 --> 02:00:19,144
我们要让这位老师帮你
We're going to have this teacher help you.

1024
02:00:19,712 --> 02:00:24,207
他会帮忙打理一切，懂吗？
He's going to help take care of all of this. Understand?

1025
02:00:24,350 --> 02:00:27,012
因为我需要你，需要你帮忙
'Cause l need you. Need your help.

1026
02:00:27,186 --> 02:00:31,145
一切条件都备齐了，过来
Got everything we need now
to build this company. Come here.

1027
02:00:38,931 --> 02:00:40,661
午安
Good afternoon.

1028
02:00:56,783 --> 02:00:58,841
-你好吗？ -很高兴再见到你
-How are you doing? -lt's nice to see you again.

1029
02:00:58,952 --> 02:01:01,750
-我们有四个人 -我马上准备
-We need four. -l'll have them right up.

1030
02:01:05,925 --> 02:01:09,359
-午安，丹尼尔 -你好，提佛
-Good afternoon, Daniel. -Tilford. Good afternoon.

1031
02:01:10,930 --> 02:01:16,197
-你好，我是提佛 -你不必用吼的
-Hello! H.M. Tilford! -You don't have to shout.

1032
02:01:18,238 --> 02:01:19,761
幸会
Pleasure.

1033
02:01:24,411 --> 02:01:26,675
小波士顿感觉很不错
lt's good to be in Little B.

1034
02:01:27,913 --> 02:01:31,212
-可以多种点树 -是啊
-Could use some rain out here. -Yeah, we could.

1035
02:01:32,085 --> 02:01:35,179
-来了 -伦敦烤肉好吃吗？
-There we go. -R.J., how's the London broil?

1036
02:01:35,354 --> 02:01:38,016
我们在这些人之前点饮料的
Believe we ordered these drinks before those people.

1037
02:01:38,158 --> 02:01:42,355
-说说看，伦敦烤肉好吃吗？ -抱歉，各位先生
-R.J., tell us. How's the London broil?
-Excuse me, gentlemen. Sorry.

1038
02:01:44,430 --> 02:01:48,367
对不起，我马上拿牛排过来
l am sorry about that, sir. l'll have your steaks right out.

1039
02:01:58,211 --> 02:02:00,805
-绿龟汤很棒 -是吗？
-So that green turtle soup is fantastic. -ls it?

1040
02:02:00,913 --> 02:02:02,541
好喝极了
lt's delicious.

1041
02:02:07,487 --> 02:02:08,545
听上去不错
Sounds good to me.

1042
02:02:08,688 --> 02:02:14,421
标准石油给我们一百万租用小波士顿的地
So Standard offered us a million
dollars for the Little Boston leases.

1043
02:02:14,527 --> 02:02:17,427
我跟提佛说他想都别想
l told H.M. Tilford where he could shove that.

1044
02:02:17,529 --> 02:02:22,159
我们跟联合石油谈妥了交易, 输油管!
And we made a deal with Union! On the pipeline!

1045
02:02:22,301 --> 02:02:25,760
还有我们地底下蕴藏的石油
And that whole ocean of oil underneath our fields.

1046
02:02:25,872 --> 02:02:27,498
-... 十五万 - 是
...$150,000. -Yes.

1047
02:02:27,640 --> 02:02:29,938
我们需要资金来开采
We needed the money to drill.

1048
02:02:30,042 --> 02:02:32,306
-这家伙是谁？ -我找过他
-Who is this guy? -l go out to meet him.

1049
02:02:32,444 --> 02:02:35,140
他挖到石油，我们想跟他谈交易
He's getting oil on the property.
We're trying to make a claim on it.

1050
02:02:35,314 --> 02:02:37,248
跟他开价一百万
Offered him a million dollars.

1051
02:02:37,350 --> 02:02:40,512
-他断然拒绝了 -我饿了
-Turned us down flat. -Well, l'm hungry.

1052
02:02:40,686 --> 02:02:45,317
橘子炸饼、马铃薯泥、青豆仁
Orange fritters, mashed potatoes, green peas.

1053
02:02:45,457 --> 02:02:47,891
-每人一份？ -我喜欢
-All the way around? -All right.

1054
02:02:50,796 --> 02:02:52,320
等等
Hold on.

1055
02:02:55,935 --> 02:02:58,164
我要你看看那边
l want you to look over there.

1056
02:02:58,304 --> 02:03:01,101
-丹尼尔，让我介绍一下... -看那边，看到没？
-Daniel, let me introduce... -Look over there. You see?

1057
02:03:01,207 --> 02:03:03,333
那是我儿子，看到他没？
That's my son. See him?

1058
02:03:03,443 --> 02:03:05,740
-看到了 -你看到了？
-Yes. -Do you see?

1059
02:03:08,081 --> 02:03:09,810
我看到他了
l see him.

1060
02:03:10,350 --> 02:03:13,251
别想教我怎么经营我的家庭
You don't tell me how to raise my family.

1061
02:03:15,354 --> 02:03:18,949
我说过别想教我怎么经营家庭
l told you not to tell me how to raise my family.

1062
02:03:20,426 --> 02:03:22,291
丹尼尔
Daniel...

1063
02:03:23,128 --> 02:03:25,063
你看到了什么？
So what do you see?

1064
02:03:26,966 --> 02:03:30,128
-交易的事我很替你高兴 -我跟联合石油谈成交易
-l'm very happy for you that the deal...
-Yes, l made a deal with Union.

1065
02:03:30,270 --> 02:03:32,636
-我儿子很高兴，他很安全 -恭喜了
-My son is happy. He's safe. -Congratulations.

1066
02:03:32,738 --> 02:03:35,867
-现在是我在照顾他，所以... -太好了
-l'm taking care of him now, so... -Excellent.

1067
02:03:37,143 --> 02:03:40,168
你看起来像个笨蛋，对吧？
You look like a fool, don't you, Tilford?

1068
02:03:44,818 --> 02:03:47,685
-对 -对
-Yes. -Yes.

1069
02:03:49,454 --> 02:03:51,184
对，你很像
Yes, you do.

1070
02:03:52,024 --> 02:03:53,753
抱歉，各位
Excuse me, gentlemen.

1071
02:03:53,859 --> 02:03:57,125
抱歉，各位，原谅他
Excuse me, gentlemen. Excuse him, gentlemen.

1072
02:04:00,667 --> 02:04:03,295
我跟你说过我会怎么做
l told you what l was going to do.

1073
02:04:13,579 --> 02:04:15,240
我的儿子
My son.

1074
02:04:32,899 --> 02:04:36,198
桑德先生，我知道你要离开这里
Mr. Sunday, l understand that you're leaving our fair community.

1075
02:04:36,368 --> 02:04:39,497
-是啊，我要去传教 -你要去哪？
-Yes, l'm going on a mission. -Where you going?

1076
02:04:39,605 --> 02:04:41,875
欧岱、塔福，之后去贝克尔斯菲
Oildale, Taft, and then on to Bakersfield.

1077
02:04:41,875 --> 02:04:42,073
我想让你知道...
Well, l want you to know...
欧岱、塔福，之后去贝克尔斯菲
Oildale, Taft, and then on to Bakersfield.

1078
02:04:42,073 --> 02:04:44,274
我想让你知道...
Well, l want you to know...

1079
02:04:44,377 --> 02:04:46,277
三刻钟时间
Three quarters of an hour.

1080
02:04:46,378 --> 02:04:47,936
你对我们贡献良多
...you done a great job for us.

1081
02:04:48,046 --> 02:04:50,981
-谢谢，你会出现在我的祈祷中 -非常感谢你
-Thank you. You will be in my prayers.
-l thank you very much.

1082
02:04:51,016 --> 02:04:54,247
联合石油公司，加州圣保拉
Union Oil Company, Santa Paula, California.

1083
02:07:03,115 --> 02:07:06,916
妇人对他说 “先生，请给我这水吧”
''The woman saith unto him, 'Sir, give me this water

1084
02:07:07,052 --> 02:07:08,179
1927年

1085
02:07:08,287 --> 02:07:12,882
“免得我再渴，也免得我再来这裹汲水”
'''and l shall thirst not, neither come hither to draw.'''

1086
02:07:44,489 --> 02:07:47,788
(向丹尼尔普兰优收取相同费用)

1087
02:08:54,694 --> 02:08:56,422
进来、进来
Come in, come in.

1088
02:09:23,155 --> 02:09:25,386
我们能单独谈谈吗？
Can we be alone?

1089
02:09:25,490 --> 02:09:29,221
这是我最亲近的伙伴，我什么都让他听
This is my closest associate. He hears everything.

1090
02:09:36,269 --> 02:09:41,332
-我想私下跟你谈 -你根本不会谈
-l'd prefer to speak to you in private. -You can't speak.

1091
02:09:41,474 --> 02:09:43,635
你何不一边挥你的手
So why don't you flap your hands about

1092
02:09:43,775 --> 02:09:47,302
一边要这家伙告诉我你去了哪里
and have what's-his-name tell me where you've been.

1093
02:09:55,320 --> 02:09:58,016
还是你以为我不知道？
Or do you think l don't know?

1094
02:10:12,505 --> 02:10:14,769
这让我很难开口
This is hard for me to say.

1095
02:10:15,841 --> 02:10:19,970
我先告诉你，我很爱你
l'll tell you first, l love you very much.

1096
02:10:23,248 --> 02:10:27,275
因为你，我学会喜爱我的工作
l've learned to love what l do because of you.

1097
02:10:30,689 --> 02:10:32,555
我要离开这里
l'm leaving here.

1098
02:10:33,960 --> 02:10:36,326
我要去墨西哥
l'm going to Mexico.

1099
02:10:36,462 --> 02:10:39,430
我要带玛丽一起走，去墨西哥
l'm taking Mary, and l'm going to Mexico.

1100
02:10:41,100 --> 02:10:43,193
我想念在户外的工作
l miss working outside.

1101
02:10:44,237 --> 02:10:46,068
我想念油田
l miss the fields.

1102
02:10:49,074 --> 02:10:51,202
只要一阵子
lt'll only be for a time,

1103
02:10:52,411 --> 02:10:54,708
让我自己去钻探石油
for me to do my own drilling

1104
02:10:56,448 --> 02:10:58,576
开始我自己的公司
and start my own company.

1105
02:11:01,587 --> 02:11:19,104
是时候...该做出改变了
lt's time to make a change.

1106
02:11:19,104 --> 02:11:21,573
这让你成为我的竞争对手
This makes you my competitor.

1107
02:11:25,578 --> 02:11:30,640
-不，不是那样的 -就是那样，孩子
-No. No, it's not like that. -lt is like that, boy.

1108
02:11:31,917 --> 02:11:33,885
你自己的公司？
Your own company, huh?

1109
02:11:34,287 --> 02:11:35,777
没错
That's right.

1110
02:11:38,123 --> 02:11:39,886
在墨西哥
ln Mexico?

1111
02:11:41,359 --> 02:11:42,417
是的
Yes.

1112
02:11:42,528 --> 02:11:47,591
你这是一大失策。为什么要这么做？
You are making such a misstep. So, what are you doing?

1113
02:11:49,635 --> 02:11:52,967
我知道你我许多事都意见相左
l know you and l have disagreed over many things.

1114
02:11:53,872 --> 02:11:58,242
我宁可你当父亲而不是事业伙伴
l'd rather keep you as my father than my partner.

1115
02:11:58,344 --> 02:11:59,810
那就说啊
Then say it.

1116
02:11:59,912 --> 02:12:01,640
如果你有话要跟我说，就说啊
lf you've got something to say to me, then say it.

1117
02:12:01,747 --> 02:12:05,376
我想听你而不是你的狗说
l'd like to hear you speak instead of your little dog.

1118
02:12:23,469 --> 02:12:26,131
我要带我太太去墨西哥
l'm going to Mexico with my wife.

1119
02:12:27,139 --> 02:12:29,265
我要离开你
l'm going away from you.

1120
02:12:35,314 --> 02:12:37,975
这并不难，对吧？
That wasn't so hard, was it?

1121
02:12:39,952 --> 02:12:42,579
以你的所作所为扼杀我们
Killing us with what you're doing.

1122
02:12:45,457 --> 02:12:48,916
你扼杀了我把你当儿子的形象
You're killing my image of you as my son.

1123
02:12:49,060 --> 02:12:52,427
你太顽固，不肯聆听
You are stubborn. You won't listen.

1124
02:12:52,597 --> 02:12:54,895
你不是我儿子
You're not my son.

1125
02:12:55,000 --> 02:12:58,162
别这么说，我知道你不是有意的
Please don't say that. l know you don't mean it.

1126
02:12:58,304 --> 02:13:02,239
这是事实，你不是我儿子，你一直都不是
lt's the truth. You're not my son. You never have been.

1127
02:13:03,609 --> 02:13:05,474
你是个...孤儿
You're an orphan!

1128
02:13:08,146 --> 02:13:10,377
你听过这个字眼吗？
Did you ever hear that word?

1129
02:13:11,917 --> 02:13:13,850
把我说的话告诉他
Tell him what l said.

1130
02:13:14,587 --> 02:13:17,488
你现在的行为就像孤儿
You operated here today like one.

1131
02:13:19,125 --> 02:13:21,592
我早该料想到这一天的
l should have seen this coming.

1132
02:13:23,095 --> 02:13:27,930
我早该知道的，过去这些年来
l should have known that,
under this all, these past years

1133
02:13:28,100 --> 02:13:31,432
你逐渐的建构了对我的仇恨
you've been building new hate for me, piece by piece.

1134
02:13:31,569 --> 02:13:35,198
我甚至不知道你是谁，因为你跟我一点都不像
l don't even know who you are
because you have none of me in you.

1135
02:13:35,306 --> 02:13:38,207
你是...别人的小孩
You're someone else's.

1136
02:13:39,612 --> 02:13:43,069
这样的愤怒、这样的存心不良
This anger. Your maliciousness.

1137
02:13:44,216 --> 02:13:47,082
跟我完全没关系
Backwards dealings with me.

1138
02:13:48,753 --> 02:13:52,712
你是沙漠中某个篮子里的孤儿
You're an orphan from a basket in the middle of the desert.

1139
02:13:55,560 --> 02:14:00,520
我认养你没别的理由，只因我需要一张小孩脸好买地
And l took you for no other reason
than l needed a sweet face to buy land.

1140
02:14:02,033 --> 02:14:03,762
你明白没？
Did you get that?

1141
02:14:05,037 --> 02:14:06,902
现在你知道了
So now you know.

1142
02:14:10,074 --> 02:14:14,408
看着我，你连废物都算不上
Look at me! You're lower than a bastard.

1143
02:14:39,371 --> 02:14:43,807
你跟我一点都不像，你只是某个篮子里的废物
You have none of me in you.
You're just a bastard from a basket.

1144
02:14:53,519 --> 02:14:57,784
感谢上帝我一点都不像你
l thank God l have none of you in me.

1145
02:15:02,661 --> 02:15:07,121
不是我儿子，只是一个没力的竞争对手
Not my son. Just a little piece of competition.

1146
02:15:09,033 --> 02:15:11,127
篮子里的废物
Bastard from a basket.

1147
02:15:13,538 --> 02:15:15,769
篮子里的废物
Bastard from a basket!

1148
02:15:24,149 --> 02:15:26,673
你是篮子里的废物
You're a bastard from a basket!

1149
02:16:29,247 --> 02:16:31,181
醒醒，丹尼尔先生
Get up, Mr. Daniel.

1150
02:16:35,421 --> 02:16:37,149
丹尼尔先生
Mr. Daniel.

1151
02:16:38,924 --> 02:16:41,518
丹尼尔先生，你有访客
Mr. Daniel, you've got a visitor.

1152
02:16:45,164 --> 02:16:47,029
醒醒，先生
Wake up, Mr. Daniel.

1153
02:16:49,735 --> 02:16:51,326
先生？
Sir?

1154
02:17:04,816 --> 02:17:06,751
你可以退下了
You can leave us now.

1155
02:17:15,059 --> 02:17:16,152
丹尼尔
Daniel.

1156
02:17:19,298 --> 02:17:20,458
丹尼尔
Daniel.

1157
02:17:23,201 --> 02:17:26,364
丹尼尔普兰优的房子失火了!
Daniel Plainview, the house is on fire!

1158
02:17:31,042 --> 02:17:34,034
丹尼尔兄弟，我是伊莱
Brother Daniel, it's Eli.

1159
02:17:44,323 --> 02:17:48,020
是的，你是
Yes, it is. Yes, it is.

1160
02:17:50,162 --> 02:17:52,061
我弄点喝的吧
l'll make us a drink.

1161
02:17:58,671 --> 02:18:01,799
你家真神奇
Your home is a miracle.

1162
02:18:03,041 --> 02:18:04,668
真美
lt's beautiful.

1163
02:18:05,343 --> 02:18:07,369
上帝庇佑它
God bless it.

1164
02:18:07,513 --> 02:18:11,505
我四处传播他的话语
l've been spreading His word far and wide.

1165
02:18:12,817 --> 02:18:14,614
四处传播
Far and wide.

1166
02:18:16,388 --> 02:18:19,152
为他旅行各处
So much travel for Him.

1167
02:18:23,861 --> 02:18:26,296
我在广播电台做过
l've been working in radio.

1168
02:18:29,001 --> 02:18:32,959
发生了...发生了好多事
Yes, so much... So much has been happening.

1169
02:18:34,005 --> 02:18:39,467
到这里，找到你，看到你还好真的很棒
To be here and find you and see you well is wonderful.

1170
02:18:39,645 --> 02:18:42,170
我们也有机会叙叙旧
And we have a chance to catch up.

1171
02:18:55,293 --> 02:18:57,387
不了，谢谢
No. Thank you so much.

1172
02:19:15,480 --> 02:19:17,141
我的兄弟
My brother.

1173
02:19:18,416 --> 02:19:21,647
丹尼尔，我的姻亲
Daniel, my brother by marriage.

1174
02:19:23,655 --> 02:19:27,784
我们真是老朋友了，这么多往日时光
We're such old friends. So much time.

1175
02:19:34,299 --> 02:19:37,393
世事多变
Things go up, things go down,

1176
02:19:37,503 --> 02:19:41,836
但至少主总是与我们同在
but at least the Lord is always around.

1177
02:19:43,407 --> 02:19:46,103
我们历经了人生起伏，不是吗？
We've seen ups and downs, haven't we?

1178
02:19:49,915 --> 02:19:52,884
你现在混得不好了，伊莱？
Are things down for you right now, Eli?

1179
02:19:54,253 --> 02:19:55,777
没有
No. No.

1180
02:19:58,090 --> 02:20:00,718
不过我的确带来了悲伤的消息
But l do come with some sad news.

1181
02:20:02,460 --> 02:20:05,191
也许你还记得班迪先生？
Perhaps you remember Mr. Bandy?

1182
02:20:07,865 --> 02:20:11,199
班迪先生蒙主恩宠了
Mr. Bandy has passed on to the Lord.

1183
02:20:12,103 --> 02:20:15,231
他于99岁辞世，上帝保佑他
He lived to be 99 years old, God bless him.

1184
02:20:15,941 --> 02:20:19,843
班迪先生有个孙子，你见过他孙子威廉吗？
Mr. Bandy has a grandson.
Have you met his grandson, William?

1185
02:20:20,845 --> 02:20:25,407
威廉班迪是我们第三启示教堂
William Bandy is one of the finest members we have

1186
02:20:25,550 --> 02:20:28,075
最优秀的成员之一
at the Church of the Third Revelation.

1187
02:20:28,219 --> 02:20:31,519
他很想到好莱坞演电影
He's eager to come to Hollywood to be in movies.

1188
02:20:32,990 --> 02:20:35,152
他的面貌非常俊秀
He is very good-looking.

1189
02:20:37,228 --> 02:20:42,256
-而我认为他会成功 -那太好了
-And l do think he will have success.
-That's wonderful.

1190
02:20:44,369 --> 02:20:47,166
你要我跟他谈吗？
Would you like me to speak with him?

1191
02:20:54,712 --> 02:20:59,445
丹尼尔，我是在问你想不想
Daniel, l'm asking if you'd like to have business

1192
02:20:59,550 --> 02:21:01,815
跟第三启示教堂一起携手
with the Church of the Third Revelation

1193
02:21:01,953 --> 02:21:06,152
开发小班迪的土地？
in developing this lease on young Bandy's 1,000-acre tract.

1194
02:21:08,627 --> 02:21:10,254
我在提议让你钻探
l'm offering you to drill

1195
02:21:10,361 --> 02:21:13,819
小波士顿未开发土地的精华之一
on one of the great undeveloped fields of Little Boston.

1196
02:21:13,966 --> 02:21:18,061
-我很乐意跟你合作 -你愿意？
-l'd be happy to work with you. -You would?

1197
02:21:19,638 --> 02:21:22,470
是啊，当然，那太好了
Yes, yes, of course. That's wonderful.

1198
02:21:22,608 --> 02:21:25,576
不过这合作有个条件
But there is one condition for this work.

1199
02:21:25,676 --> 02:21:27,166
好的
All right.

1200
02:21:29,281 --> 02:21:32,772
我要你告诉我你是个假先知
l'd like you to tell me that you are a false prophet.

1201
02:21:38,156 --> 02:21:43,559
我要你告诉我你是，以前也是一个假先知
l'd like you to tell me that you are,
and have been a false prophet.

1202
02:21:44,763 --> 02:21:47,129
还有上帝是个迷信
And that God is a superstition.

1203
02:21:53,272 --> 02:21:55,068
那可是谎言
But that's a lie.

1204
02:21:57,843 --> 02:22:00,403
那是谎言，我说不出口
lt's a lie. l cannot say it.

1205
02:22:14,692 --> 02:22:17,093
-我们何时可以开始钻探？ -很快
-When can we begin to drill? -Very soon.

1206
02:22:17,194 --> 02:22:18,855
油井要多久才能量产？
How long will it take to bring in the well?

1207
02:22:18,963 --> 02:22:20,828
应该不用多久
lt shouldn't take long.

1208
02:22:20,966 --> 02:22:24,264
我想要十万签约金
l would like a $100,000 signing bonus,

1209
02:22:24,403 --> 02:22:27,600
加上你欠我的五千元本利
plus the five that is owed to me with interest.

1210
02:22:28,307 --> 02:22:30,103
那很公平
That's only fair.

1211
02:22:35,846 --> 02:22:40,613
我是假先知，上帝也是迷信
l am a false prophet, and God is a superstition.

1212
02:22:40,786 --> 02:22:43,754
如果你这么想，我就说
lf that's what you believe, then l will say it.

1213
02:22:43,854 --> 02:22:47,313
-真心诚意的说 -丹尼尔
-Say it like you mean it. -Daniel.

1214
02:22:47,893 --> 02:22:50,225
就像你讲道一样
Say it like it's your sermon.

1215
02:22:53,397 --> 02:22:55,024
别笑
Don't smile.

1216
02:23:00,806 --> 02:23:02,706
我是假先知
l am a false prophet.

1217
02:23:02,808 --> 02:23:06,140
-上帝是迷信 -你何不站起来
-God is a superstition. -Why don't you stand up?

1218
02:23:09,246 --> 02:23:11,237
把杯子放下
Put your glass down.

1219
02:23:23,361 --> 02:23:26,957
我是假先知
l am a false prophet.

1220
02:23:27,065 --> 02:23:30,158
-上帝是迷信 -伊莱，停
-God is a superstition. -Eli, stop.

1221
02:23:30,301 --> 02:23:35,672
想像这里是你的教堂，你的教徒满坑满谷
Just imagine this is your church here
and you have a full congregation, so...

1222
02:23:38,209 --> 02:23:41,976
我是假先知，上帝是迷信
l am a false prophet. God is a superstition.

1223
02:23:42,079 --> 02:23:43,740
再说一次
Say it again.

1224
02:23:44,716 --> 02:23:48,618
我是假先知，上帝是迷信
l am a false prophet. God is a superstition.

1225
02:23:48,719 --> 02:23:49,879
后面的听不见
They can't hear you at the back.

1226
02:23:49,987 --> 02:23:53,320
我是假先知，上帝是迷信
l am a false prophet. God is a superstition.

1227
02:23:53,492 --> 02:23:54,549
再说一次
Say it again.

1228
02:23:54,658 --> 02:23:59,289
我是假先知，上帝是迷信
l am a false prophet! God is a superstition!

1229
02:23:59,397 --> 02:24:01,093
再说一次
Say it again.

1230
02:24:01,199 --> 02:24:04,930
我是假先知，上帝是迷信
l am a false prophet! God is a superstition!

1231
02:24:06,138 --> 02:24:08,469
那里的地已经被钻探过了
Those areas have been drilled.

1232
02:24:11,610 --> 02:24:13,042
什么？
What?

1233
02:24:13,145 --> 02:24:15,738
那里的地，已经钻探过了
Those areas, they've been drilled.

1234
02:24:17,349 --> 02:24:20,876
-不，并没有 -有的
-No, they haven't. -Yes, it's...

1235
02:24:20,986 --> 02:24:22,351
那叫汲取
lt's called drainage, Eli.

1236
02:24:22,453 --> 02:24:27,254
我拥有附近的地，当然就能得到下面的东西
See, l own everything around it, so,
of course, l get what's underneath it.

1237
02:24:28,760 --> 02:24:31,888
不过那里没有钻油井
But there are no derricks there.

1238
02:24:32,030 --> 02:24:34,430
我说的是班迪的地，你明白吗？
This is the Bandy tract. Do you understand?

1239
02:24:34,532 --> 02:24:36,523
伊莱，你明白吗？
Do you understand, Eli?

1240
02:24:37,269 --> 02:24:40,466
不止是那样，你明白吗？
That's more to the point. Do you understand?

1241
02:24:40,604 --> 02:24:45,975
我喝了你的水，我每天都喝
l drink your water. l drink it up every day.

1242
02:24:46,977 --> 02:24:51,244
我喝了班迪那块地的羔羊宝血
l drink the blood of Lamb from Bandy's tract.

1243
02:24:56,487 --> 02:24:58,581
你可以坐下了
You can sit down again.

1244
02:25:16,774 --> 02:25:18,105
丹尼尔
Daniel.

1245
02:25:21,413 --> 02:25:22,402
丹尼尔
Daniel.

1246
02:25:26,283 --> 02:25:27,876
求求你
Please.

1247
02:25:30,221 --> 02:25:34,556
-我很绝望 -我知道
-l am in desperate times. -l know.

1248
02:25:34,692 --> 02:25:37,490
-我需要朋友 -当然，你需要
-l need a friend. -Yes. Of course, you do.

1249
02:25:37,896 --> 02:25:39,487
我有罪
l've sinned.

1250
02:25:41,233 --> 02:25:44,326
我需要帮忙，我是罪人
l need help. l'm a sinner.

1251
02:25:44,435 --> 02:25:49,066
我让恶魔以我无法想像的方法掌握住我
l've let the devil grab hold of me
in ways l never imagined.

1252
02:25:49,207 --> 02:25:50,605
我满身是罪
l'm so full of sin.

1253
02:25:50,709 --> 02:25:53,974
上帝有时会挑战我们，不是吗？
The Lord sometimes challenges us, doesn't He, Eli?

1254
02:25:54,111 --> 02:25:56,102
-是的，他会 -是的，他会
-Yes, He does, Daniel. -Yes, He does.

1255
02:25:56,213 --> 02:25:58,738
是的，他会
Yes, He does!

1256
02:25:58,916 --> 02:26:00,816
是的，他会
Yes, He does!

1257
02:26:02,086 --> 02:26:07,683
他完全没有警告我最近的经济恐慌
He's completely failed to alert me
to the recent panic in our economy.

1258
02:26:07,825 --> 02:26:09,952
-而这一切... -亲爱的
-And this... -Oh, dear.

1259
02:26:10,094 --> 02:26:16,727
我一定要开发这块地，我一定要、一定要开发
l must have this, Daniel. l must, l must, l must have this.

1260
02:26:16,902 --> 02:26:19,165
我的投资都...
My investments have...

1261
02:26:19,271 --> 02:26:24,334
我不逼你，不过若我能抓住上帝帮助的手
Daniel, l won't bore you, but if l could
grab the Lord's hand for help l would,

1262
02:26:24,476 --> 02:26:27,343
他常行如此神迹
but He does these things all the time.

1263
02:26:27,478 --> 02:26:31,380
他现出了那些神迹，我们等待...
These mysteries that He presents, and while we wait...

1264
02:26:32,683 --> 02:26:34,844
我们等待他的指示
While we wait for His word!

1265
02:26:34,986 --> 02:26:37,950
因为你不是上帝的兄弟，伊莱
Because you're not the chosen brother, Eli.

1266
02:26:40,358 --> 02:26:44,157
上帝的兄弟是保罗
'Twas Paul who was chosen.

1267
02:26:45,030 --> 02:26:47,965
他告诉我地的事，你只是个笨蛋
He found me and told me
about your land. You're just a fool.

1268
02:26:48,066 --> 02:26:50,933
-你为什么要说保罗？ -我做了你兄弟做不到的事
-Why are you talking about Paul?
-l did what your brother couldn't.

1269
02:26:51,036 --> 02:26:53,527
-别对我说这个 -我让你破产还打了你
-Don't say this to me.
-l broke you and l beat you.

1270
02:26:54,471 --> 02:26:57,270
保罗先把你的事告诉了我
lt was Paul told me about you.

1271
02:26:57,375 --> 02:27:01,834
他才是先知，他才有脑袋，他早知道那里有什么
He's the prophet. He's the smart one.
He knew what was there

1272
02:27:01,979 --> 02:27:04,345
他找我去把地下的东西挖出来
and he found me to take it out of the ground.

1273
02:27:04,481 --> 02:27:07,507
知道最好笑的是什么吗？听着
Know what the funny thing is? Listen, listen.

1274
02:27:08,386 --> 02:27:12,322
我当面给了他一万元现金，就这样
l paid him $10,000 cash in hand. Just like that.

1275
02:27:13,358 --> 02:27:16,656
他现在拥有自己的公司，不错的小事业
He has his own company now. Prosperous little business.

1276
02:27:16,795 --> 02:27:20,322
三口井量产，每周五千元
Three wells producing, $5,000 a week.

1277
02:27:22,367 --> 02:27:26,166
别哀嚎了，你这个爱哭鬼。别胡闹了
Stop crying, you sniveling ass. Stop your nonsense.

1278
02:27:27,371 --> 02:27:31,273
- 你只是个胎盘，伊莱 - 不
-You're just the afterbirth, Eli.
-No.

1279
02:27:31,408 --> 02:27:34,037
是母体排出的秽物
That slithered out
on your mother's filth.

1280
02:27:34,145 --> 02:27:35,510
不
No.

1281
02:27:35,613 --> 02:27:39,778
他们应该把你放进罐子里当装饰品
They should've put you in a glass jar on the mantelpiece.

1282
02:27:41,486 --> 02:27:44,818
保罗在吸奶时，你在哪里？
Where were you when Paul was suckling at his mother's teat?

1283
02:27:44,989 --> 02:27:46,513
你在哪里？
Where were you?

1284
02:27:46,625 --> 02:27:51,358
谁在哺育你，可怜的伊莱？班迪家的母猪？
Who was nursing you, poor Eli?
One of Bandy's sows?

1285
02:27:51,462 --> 02:27:54,363
那块地已经干了，你无能为力
That land has been had.
Nothing you can do about it. lt's gone.

1286
02:27:54,466 --> 02:27:56,661
-你先看看这块地... -你输了
-lf you would just take this lease... -You lose.

1287
02:27:56,768 --> 02:27:59,965
干了
Drainage!

1288
02:28:01,005 --> 02:28:04,601
干了，伊莱，单纯的家伙
Drainage, Eli, you boy.

1289
02:28:05,744 --> 02:28:08,679
被吸干了，真对不起
Drained dry. l'm so sorry.

1290
02:28:09,880 --> 02:28:12,007
如果你有一杯奶昔
lf you have a milkshake

1291
02:28:13,084 --> 02:28:14,846
我也有一杯奶昔
and l have a milkshake,

1292
02:28:14,952 --> 02:28:18,115
我还有吸管，就在这，看到没？
and l have a straw, there it is.
That's the straw, you see?

1293
02:28:18,255 --> 02:28:19,780
看着
Watch it.

1294
02:28:21,259 --> 02:28:28,188
现在我的吸管跑过房间
Now my straw reaches across the room

1295
02:28:29,467 --> 02:28:32,264
开始吸你的奶昔
and starts to drink your milkshake.

1296
02:28:33,203 --> 02:28:37,004
我喝了你的奶昔
l drink your milkshake!

1297
02:28:39,209 --> 02:28:42,667
-我喝光了 -别欺负我，丹尼尔
-l drink it up! -Don't bully me, Daniel.

1298
02:28:45,416 --> 02:28:50,649
你真以为你的歌舞和迷信能够帮你？
Did you think your song and dance and
your superstition would help you, Eli?

1299
02:28:50,754 --> 02:28:55,385
我才是先知，我才是上帝选上的
l am the Third Revelation. l am who the Lord has chosen.

1300
02:28:57,594 --> 02:28:59,893
-丹尼尔！-因为我比你聪明
-Daniel! -Because l'm smarter than you!

1301
02:29:00,031 --> 02:29:01,691
我比你老
l'm older!

1302
02:29:02,334 --> 02:29:04,130
我是你的老朋友
l'm your old friend, Daniel!

1303
02:29:04,235 --> 02:29:06,635
-我不是假先知 -救救我!救救我!
-l'm not a false prophet... -Help me! Help me!

1304
02:29:06,737 --> 02:29:09,002
你这个爱哭鬼
...you sniveling boy!

1305
02:29:09,106 --> 02:29:15,773
我才是先知，我才是先知
l am the Third Revelation! l am the Third Revelation!

1306
02:29:15,879 --> 02:29:18,849
-我说过我会吃了你 -我们是一家人
-l told you l would eat you. -We're family!

1307
02:29:18,983 --> 02:29:23,442
-我说过我会吃光你 -我们是兄弟!我们是兄弟!
-l told you l would eat you up!
-We're brothers! We're brothers!

1308
02:29:30,528 --> 02:29:33,325
丹尼尔，原谅我，我求你
Daniel, please forgive me. l beg you.

1309
02:29:37,001 --> 02:29:39,093
就是这样，就是这样
That's it. That's it.

1310
02:30:41,466 --> 02:30:43,331
丹尼尔先生？
Mr. Daniel?

1311
02:30:50,908 --> 02:30:52,536
我完了
l'm finished.

1312
02:31:08,192 --> 02:31:15,121
黑金企业

1313
02:37:53,129 --> 02:38:00,058
黑金企业

